pertoire is extremely unique from Isuzu Vietnam</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5722" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5722" title="4" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/04/4-e1367040223571.png" alt="" width="560" height="435" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">The performance of the Isuzu superset impressive collection of handmade and Miss Isuzu was also voted to end the program.</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id="attachment_5723" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><em><img class="size-full wp-image-5723" title="5" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/04/5-e1367040297767.png" alt="" width="560" height="421" /></em>\n<p class="wp-caption-text">Customers first 30,000, 29,999 and 30,001 are awarded agency Anqing special gifts instead of gratitude. At the same time customers are also participating in the lucky draw 3 GPS locator journey from Isuzu Vietnam. <br /> <br />Isuzu Vietnam will continue its commitment to provide products and services with the best quality to express gratitude for the confidence of our customers, and to contribute more to the development of business customers as well as for the economy and society of Vietnam.</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5724" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5724 " title="6" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/04/6-e1367040384195.png" alt="" width="560" height="404" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">The program also honored with the presence of Isuzu Vietnam Directorate and Directorate of Southern Isuzu dealer <br /> <br />All information about the products please contact Isuzu System of Isuzu authorized dealers nationwide.</p>\n</div>');
