INSERT INTO `events_lang` VALUES(58, 'ENG', 'ISUZU TRUCK DRIVERS WITH TEST AND FEEL THE DIFFERENCE', '<p>In recent times, Isuzu Vietnam has implemented many consecutive Test drive the program to introduce the Isuzu product closer to customers across the country. 04 On 24 January 2013, the high quality of products Isuzu was very pleased with your customer to the Mekong Delta in general and customers in particular Kien Giang province through the test drive program Isuzu vehicles are held at City Coffee Corner - Snorkeling, Rach.</p>\n<div id="attachment_5807" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5807" title="0" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/05/0-e1369787800792.png" alt="" width="560" height="436" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">Panorama area events on 05/24/2013 <br /> <br />Come to this program, Isuzu Vietnam and Khanh agents are pleased to introduce the key vehicles including heavy trucks Isuzu FVM, FVZ ben, light trucks and special QKR, and the presence of line best pickup priority Vietnam market today - debuted in March last - Isuzu D-MAX Completely new.</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5808" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5808" title="4 xe" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/05/4-xe-e1369787957102.png" alt="" width="560" height="741" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">The FVM Trucks, FVZ ben, QKR pickup truck and all-new D-Max is to the customer in the event of Kien Giang <br /> <br />FVM cars are a lot of customers in this area of interest based on the quality, reliability and fuel-saving capabilities superior long known. Therefore, the long-24T heavy trucks were super large customers in selected areas to test drive handedly experience the real advantages of Vietnamese products.</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5809" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5809" title="2" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/05/2-e1369788137627.png" alt="" width="560" height="453" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">FVM cars are a lot of customers in this area of interest based on the quality, durability and ability unsurpassed fuel economy. <br /> <br />After the program, the FVM has received a lot of positive feedback from customers. Besides, within the framework of this program, customers can experience QKR line of Isuzu light trucks. QKR light trucks with a load capacity of up to 1t9 1T4. Although new on the market from Vietnam in early 2012 but has been warmly received customers thanks to its superior features with affordable, suitable for all customers.</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5810" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5810" title="IMG_1882" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/05/IMG_1882-e1369788421429.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="420" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">QKR customers test drive <br /> <br />In addition, as outlined above, in response to the great interest of the client D-max car entirely new, Isuzu Vietnam brought in Kien Giang customers the opportunity to experience actual hands behind driving a pickup line with the most advanced features on the Vietnamese market today are designed with exterior perfect, luxurious interior, convenient, as well as strength and absolute safety during operation.</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5811" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5811" title="4" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/05/4-e1369788490115.png" alt="" width="560" height="428" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">New D-Max received a lot of attention from customers <br /> <br />Not only have the opportunity to test drive and experience, to attend this program, the driver has the opportunity to contribute ideas and advice received enthusiastically from Isuzu staff for any questions related What is in place.</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5813" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5813" title="5" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/05/51-e1369788649441.png" alt="" width="560" height="741" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">Clients receive counseling as well as many enthusiastic attractive gifts from Isuzu <br /> <br />Through the program the customer actually has a sharper look on Isuzu vehicles as well as discuss some specific knowledge about the product. Isuzu Vietnam sincerely grateful for the enthusiastic participation of customers despite bad weather with heavy rain and high winds. The program must end sooner than expected, but still attracted more than 200 visitors per tour, which has about 100 customers participated test drive.</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5814" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5814" title="6" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/05/6-e1369788745986.png" alt="" width="560" height="741" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">Isuzu Vietnam sincerely grateful for the enthusiastic participation of customers despite bad weather with heavy rain and high winds. <br /> <br />We wish you lots of success! <br /> <br />Please contact official system Isuzu Dealers nationwide for more details.</p>\n</div>');
