age-5832" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/06/DSC_1111-e1370860803453.jpg" alt="" width="561" height="369" /></dt><dd class="wp-caption-dd">The spectacular performance of the Isuzu D-MAX prison entirely new</dd></dl></div>\n<p>Isuzu brand new imported CBU from Thailand, the Isuzu D-MAX is equipped with completely new diesel 4-cylinder 2.999cc capacity for maximum power 136 PS at 3,400 r / min and torque maximum torque of 294Nm at 1,400 to 3,000 revolutions / minute latest generation maximizes performance great fuel level (minimum level of average fuel consumption 7l/100km (fuel consumption may change depending on the actual operating conditions of the vehicle).</p>\n<div class="mceTemp mceIEcenter"  center;"><dl id="attachment_5833" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><dt class="wp-caption-dt"><img class="size-full wp-image-5833" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/06/1-e1370877616307.png" alt="" width="561" height="374" /></dt><dd class="wp-caption-dd"><span>The Off-road terrain vehicle</span></dd></dl></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="mceTemp mceIEcenter"><dl id="attachment_5836" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><dt class="wp-caption-dt"><img class="size-full wp-image-5836" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/06/DSC_1062-e1370877718652.jpg" alt="" width="561" height="373" /></dt><dd class="wp-caption-dd">In particular, the challenge is sloping challenge that involved customers test drive the most impressive - showing great traction capabilities of the all-new D-MAX</dd></dl></div>\n<div class="mceTemp mceIEcenter"><dl id="attachment_5837" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><dt class="wp-caption-dt"><img class="size-full wp-image-5837" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/06/2-e1370877903629.png" alt="" width="561" height="205" /></dt><dd class="wp-caption-dd">Customers have a team of technical experts Isuzu dedicated guidance.</dd></dl></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="mceTemp mceIEcenter"><dl id="attachment_5