INSERT INTO `events_lang` VALUES(62, 'ENG', 'ISUZU VIETNAM ORGANIZATIONS Customer Appreciation Ceremony in Lam Dong Province', '<p>Over the road 18 years since its establishment, Isuzu Vietnam with the motto "Always at your party" has constantly strived to provide our customers the best quality products and after sales service at priority. Already more than 30,000 cars Isuzu is distributed to customers all over the country. This figure has shown impressive customer confidence in the quality, durability and fuel savings of proven Isuzu products. <br /> <br />So, on 29/6 last, Isuzu Vietnam solemn tribute ceremony at Sammy Da Lat, in order to express gratitude for more than 200 customers have trusted and supported products Isuzu products over time.</p>\n<div id="attachment_5909" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5909" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/hfh-e1372763523153.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="420" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">Numerous customers in Lam Dong province attended the intimate dinner Isuzu Vietnam</p>\n</div>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5885" title="1" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/1-e1372757118745.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="420" /></p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5886" title="Untitled" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Untitled-e1372757505452.png" alt="" width="560" height="520" />At the party, guests also enjoy a lot of unique items and participating in the lucky draw from Isuzu Vietnam with the prize car repairs free shares worth 5,000,000, respectively, 10,000,000 and 15,000,000.<img class="size-full wp-image-5887" title="lucky draw" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/lucky-draw-e1372757635570.png" alt="" width="560" height="741" /></p>\n<div id="attachment_5887" class="wp-caption aligncenter">\n<p class="wp-caption-text">03 lucky guests in the party had won the first, second, third slip sweepstakes repair maintenance-free $ 15 million, 10 million and 5 million from Isuzu Vietnam</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id="attachment_5888" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5888" title="performance" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/performance-e1372758196954.png" alt="" width="560" height="560" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">The unique repertoire of games and fun for intimate dinner at Sammy Da Lat <br /> <br />Besides Vietnam Isuzu also gives customers the opportunity to experience the advantages of Vietnam on Isuzu product line through the F-series test drive and new Dmax.</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5899" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5899" title="DISPLAY" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/DISPLAY-e1372759561451.png" alt="" width="560" height="470" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">FVM 03 cars, and D-max FVZ entirely new Isuzu Vietnam offers programs and test drive displayed in Da Lat <br /> <br />F-Series cars appeared in Vietnam since 1997. This car is equipped with the Isuzu D-Core direct fuel injection cooling intake air to help power vehicles increased by 23%, saving more than 18%, quieter and faster speed than the engine can not commonrail. In addition, the car can reach environmental standards Euro 2 - more environmentally friendly. Because Japanese quality standards and high operating efficiency, ensure economic benefits, Isuzu F-Series has earned the confidence of our customers.</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5890" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5890" title="6" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/6-e1372758619519.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="420" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">Isuzu FVM cars at super long 24 tons <br /> <br />Isuzu brand new imported CBU from Thailand, the Isuzu D-MAX is equipped with completely new diesel 4-cylinder 2.999cc capacity for maximum power 136 PS at 3,400 r / min and torque maximum torque of 294Nm at 1,400 to 3,000 revolutions / minute latest generation maximizes performance great fuel level (minimum level of average fuel consumption 7l/100km (fuel consumption may change depending on the actual operating conditions of the vehicle).</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5891" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5891" title="D-max test drive" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/D-max-test-drive-e1372759793278.png" alt="" width="560" height="560" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">Area terrain test drive for the car brand new D-max is the Isuzu Vietnam expert installation adventurous and fun at Dalat Golf Valley</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5908" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5908" title="IMG_20130702_175031" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/IMG_20130702_175031-e1372762621424.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="420" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">The test drive new D-max was held in Da Lat Golf Valley <br /> <br />Challenge slope represents excellent road holding ability of the car entirely new D-max.</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5892" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5892" title="8" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/8-e1372758787169.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="420" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">The challenge can sloping porch road traction and excellent ability to balance the car''s all-new D-max <br /> <br />Within 2 days 29 &amp; 30/6, Isuzu Vietnam has received more than 120 visitors register shrugged test drive and get positive feedback for above two cars.</p>\n</div>\n<div id="attachment_5893" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5893" title="9" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/9-e1372758877288.png" alt="" width="560" height="560" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">Customers participating car test drive and learn new Dmax</p>\n</div>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5911" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/tuvan-e1372763924475.png" alt="" width="560" height="741" /></p>\n<div id="attachment_5896" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-5896" title="teabreak" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/teabreak-e1372759155710.png" alt="" width="560" height="560" />\n<p class="wp-caption-text">Food and soft drinks for guests to attend the program</p>\n</div>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5894" title="10" src="../../../../../wp-content/uploads/2013/07/10-e1372758958686.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="420" /></p>\n<p>All information about the products please contact Isuzu system nearest Isuzu dealer.</p>');
